---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Attire">

  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <section class="attire-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="attire-header-inner">
        <span class="eyebrow">Article No. III · The Fashion Desk</span>
        <h1 class="attire-title">Attire</h1>
        <div class="rule-double" style="max-width: 220px; margin: 1.5rem auto;"></div>
        <p class="attire-subtitle">
          A short dispatch on what to wear, with notes from the editors.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DRESS CODE HEADLINE -->
  <section class="dresscode-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="dresscode-card">
        <div class="dresscode-corner tl"></div>
        <div class="dresscode-corner tr"></div>
        <div class="dresscode-corner bl"></div>
        <div class="dresscode-corner br"></div>

        <span class="section-label" style="color: var(--dispatch-terracotta);">The Dress Code</span>
        <h2 class="dresscode-word">Formal</h2>
        <div class="divider" style="max-width: 200px; margin: 1rem auto;">
          <div class="divider-line"></div>
          <div class="divider-diamond"></div>
          <div class="divider-line"></div>
        </div>
        <p class="dresscode-blurb">
          Floor-length gowns, cocktail dresses, dark suits, or tuxedos.
          Dress as you would for an evening at the opera, the symphony, or
          a wedding that intends to be remembered.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PALETTE SECTION -->
  <section class="palette-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="palette-intro">
        <span class="section-label">The Wedding Palette</span>
        <h3>Tones for the occasion</h3>
        <p>Guests are warmly invited, though by no means required, to draw
        from the palette below. Consider it a friendly suggestion from the
        fashion desk, not a decree.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="palette-grid">
        <div class="palette-card">
          <div class="palette-color" style="background: #fbe45b;"></div>
          <div class="palette-meta">
            <span class="palette-name">Dispatch Yellow</span>
            <span class="palette-hex">#FBE45B</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="palette-card">
          <div class="palette-color" style="background: #c4aa23;"></div>
          <div class="palette-meta">
            <span class="palette-name">Editor's Ochre</span>
            <span class="palette-hex">#C4AA23</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="palette-card">
          <div class="palette-color" style="background: #a6d0c8;"></div>
          <div class="palette-meta">
            <span class="palette-name">Mint Veranda</span>
            <span class="palette-hex">#A6D0C8</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="palette-card">
          <div class="palette-color" style="background: #2c7c94;"></div>
          <div class="palette-meta">
            <span class="palette-name">Hudson Teal</span>
            <span class="palette-hex">#2C7C94</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="palette-card">
          <div class="palette-color" style="background: #a65852;"></div>
          <div class="palette-meta">
            <span class="palette-name">Reception Terracotta</span>
            <span class="palette-hex">#A65852</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DEPARTMENTS / SUGGESTIONS -->
  <section class="departments">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="departments-grid">

        <article class="dept-card">
          <span class="dept-kicker">For Ladies</span>
          <h3>An evening of finery</h3>
          <div class="rule-double" style="max-width: 70px; margin: 0.8rem 0 1.4rem;"></div>
          <ul class="dept-list">
            <li><strong>Long gowns</strong> in the wedding palette, or in classic black, ivory, or navy.</li>
            <li><strong>Cocktail dresses</strong> at or below the knee, in a refined cut.</li>
            <li><strong>Jumpsuits</strong> are welcomed, provided they read as formal.</li>
            <li><strong>Wraps and shawls</strong> recommended for the evening air.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="dept-card">
          <span class="dept-kicker">For Gentlemen</span>
          <h3>A study in tailoring</h3>
          <div class="rule-double" style="max-width: 70px; margin: 0.8rem 0 1.4rem;"></div>
          <ul class="dept-list">
            <li><strong>Dark suits</strong> in charcoal, navy, or deep teal are most welcome.</li>
            <li><strong>Tuxedos</strong> are appropriate and encouraged.</li>
            <li><strong>Ties</strong> are required. A pocket square is a kindness.</li>
            <li><strong>Polished oxfords or loafers</strong>, please, never sneakers.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NOTES -->
  <section class="notes-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="notes-card">
        <span class="section-label" style="color: var(--dispatch-yellow);">From the Editor</span>
        <h3 style="color: var(--dispatch-yellow);">A few practical notes</h3>
        <div class="notes-grid">
          <div class="note">
            <span class="note-no">01</span>
            <p>The ceremony will take place outdoors at the East Garden Pavilion. The lawn is soft. Stilettos may sink. Block heels and flats are the wiser choice.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="note">
            <span class="note-no">02</span>
            <p>The reception begins indoors at 6:00 PM. Evenings in the Hudson Valley can turn cool, even in June. A wrap, a shawl, or a tailored jacket is a thoughtful addition.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="note">
            <span class="note-no">03</span>
            <p>Out of long-standing tradition, we ask that guests refrain from wearing white, ivory, or cream. The bride has already claimed those shades for the day.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="note">
            <span class="note-no">04</span>
            <p>If you find yourself uncertain, dress as though you might be photographed. You will be.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CLOSING -->
  <section class="closing-section">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
      <p class="closing-quote">"Be yourself, beautifully."</p>
      <p class="closing-attr">The Fashion Desk</p>
      <a href="/rsvp" class="btn btn-filled" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">RSVP for the Evening</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* PAGE HEADER */
  .attire-header {
    background: var(--dispatch-yellow);
    padding: 5rem 2rem 4rem;
    border-bottom: 3px double var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .attire-header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 16px;
    border: 2px solid var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .attire-header-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .attire-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .attire-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--dispatch-teal);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* DRESS CODE HEADLINE */
  .dresscode-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: var(--dispatch-yellow);
  }
  .dresscode-card {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--dispatch-cream);
    border: 3px solid var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
    padding: 4rem 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .dresscode-corner {
    position: absolute;
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    border-color: var(--dispatch-terracotta);
    border-style: solid;
  }
  .dresscode-corner.tl { top: 10px; left: 10px; border-width: 2.5px 0 0 2.5px; }
  .dresscode-corner.tr { top: 10px; right: 10px; border-width: 2.5px 2.5px 0 0; }
  .dresscode-corner.bl { bottom: 10px; left: 10px; border-width: 0 0 2.5px 2.5px; }
  .dresscode-corner.br { bottom: 10px; right: 10px; border-width: 0 2.5px 2.5px 0; }

  .dresscode-word {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(4.5rem, 12vw, 8rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
  }
  .dresscode-blurb {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* PALETTE SECTION */
  .palette-section {
    background: var(--dispatch-mint);
    padding: 5rem 0;
    border-top: 1.5px solid var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
  }
  .palette-intro {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }
  .palette-intro h3 { margin: 0.4rem 0 1rem; }
  .palette-intro p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
  }
  .palette-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .palette-card {
    background: var(--dispatch-cream);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease;
  }
  .palette-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .palette-color {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
  }
  .palette-meta {
    padding: 0.85rem 0.75rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .palette-name {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .palette-hex {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--dispatch-teal);
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }

  /* DEPARTMENTS */
  .departments {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: var(--dispatch-yellow);
  }
  .departments-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .dept-card {
    background: var(--dispatch-cream);
    border: 2px solid var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
  }
  .dept-kicker {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--dispatch-terracotta);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .dept-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    color: var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
    margin: 0.4rem 0 0;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .dept-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .dept-list li {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
    padding: 0.7rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--dispatch-teal);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .dept-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .dept-list strong {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dispatch-terracotta);
  }

  /* NOTES */
  .notes-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: var(--dispatch-yellow);
  }
  .notes-card {
    background: var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
    border: 3px solid var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
    padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .notes-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--dispatch-yellow);
    opacity: 0.35;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .notes-card .section-label { color: var(--dispatch-yellow); }
  .notes-card h3 {
    color: var(--dispatch-yellow);
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
  }
  .notes-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .note {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .note-no {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    color: var(--dispatch-terracotta);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    min-width: 50px;
  }
  .note p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--dispatch-cream);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* CLOSING */
  .closing-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: var(--dispatch-yellow);
  }
  .closing-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
    color: var(--dispatch-teal-deep);
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .closing-attr {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--dispatch-terracotta);
  }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .palette-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .departments-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .notes-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .palette-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .dresscode-card { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
    .attire-header::before { inset: 12px; }
  }
</style>